1937;;Slaves in Bondage;;American;;Elmer Clifton;;Lona Andre, Wheeler Oakman, Florence Dudley;;drama, exploitation;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Slaves_in_Bondage;;The film tells the tale of how naive country girls are lured to the big city with the promise of employment only to be abducted and forced to work as prostitutes in decadent, high-class brothels.